stian, in the State. In "Metro" A Chinese expatriate was reportedly killed by suspected gunmen, who disarmed some policemen at a mining site in Iboko, Izzi Local Government Area of Ebonyi State. In "News" Suspected gunmen have disarmed some policemen and killed a chinese expatriate at a mining site in Iboko, Izzi Local Government Area of Ebonyi. SP Chris Anyanwu, Spokesperson, Police Command in Ebonyi, told journalists that the incident was yet to be confirmed by the command. “It has not been confirmed, but… In "News"